#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.yv.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.yv"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:1 of
msgid "Bessel function of the second kind of real order and complex argument."
msgstr "实数阶和复数参数的第二类贝塞尔函数。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.yv.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:3 of
msgid "Order (float)."
msgstr "阶数（浮点数）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:5 of
msgid "Argument (float or complex)."
msgstr "参数（浮点数或复数）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:7 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function results"
msgstr "用于函数结果的可选输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.yv.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:10 of
msgid "**Y** -- Value of the Bessel function of the second kind, :math:`Y_v(x)`."
msgstr "**Y** -- 第二类贝塞尔函数的值，:math:`Y_v(x)`。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.yv.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:15 of
msgid ":py:obj:`yve`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:16 of
msgid ":math:`Y_v` with leading exponential behavior stripped off."
msgstr "去除主导指数行为后的 :math:`Y_v`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:18 of
msgid ":py:obj:`y0`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:19 of
msgid "faster implementation of this function for order 0"
msgstr "该函数在阶数为 0 时的快速实现"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`y1`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:22 of
msgid "faster implementation of this function for order 1"
msgstr "该函数在阶数为 1 时的快速实现"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:25 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:26 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"For positive `v` values, the computation is carried out using the AMOS "
"[1]_ `zbesy` routine, which exploits the connection to the Hankel Bessel "
"functions :math:`H_v^{(1)}` and :math:`H_v^{(2)}`,"
msgstr ""
"对于正的 `v` 值，使用 AMOS [1]_ 的 `zbesy` 程序进行计算，它利用了与汉克尔"
"贝塞尔函数 :math:`H_v^{(1)}` 和 :math:`H_v^{(2)}` 的关系，"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:30 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Y_v(z) = \\frac{1}{2\\imath} (H_v^{(1)} - H_v^{(2)}).\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:32 of
msgid "For negative `v` values the formula,"
msgstr "对于负的 `v` 值，使用以下公式，"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:34 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Y_{-v}(z) = Y_v(z) \\cos(\\pi v) + J_v(z) \\sin(\\pi v)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:36 of
msgid ""
"is used, where :math:`J_v(z)` is the Bessel function of the first kind, "
"computed using the AMOS routine `zbesj`.  Note that the second term is "
"exactly zero for integer `v`; to improve accuracy the second term is "
"explicitly omitted for `v` values such that `v = floor(v)`."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`J_v(z)` 是第一类贝塞尔函数，通过 AMOS 程序 `zbesj` 计算。注意"
"第二项在整数 `v` 时恰好为零；为了提高精度，当 `v = floor(v)` 时，第二项被"
"显式省略。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:42 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yv:43 of
msgid ""
"Donald E. Amos, \"AMOS, A Portable Package for Bessel Functions of a "
"Complex Argument and Nonnegative Order\", http://netlib.org/amos/"
msgstr ""

